    <p>
The level of care received by a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_neonate">Neonate</xref>
 during a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_neonatal_level_of_care_period">Neonatal Level Of Care Period</xref>. For all 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_ward">WARDS</xref>
